Hold-to-confirm offer buttons, cart price parity, relationship-aware CHIM

- Offer window: Submit (gold) and Intimidate (red) buttons now fill on hold
  and commit when full; toggle + customizable duration in the SKSE menu.
  Gated every commit path (ProcessMessage, input sink, mouse, FxDelegate).
- Fill bar reveals via _alpha (clips are hidden by a ColorTransform, not _visible).
- Cart panel now applies the standing price multiplier so its totals/lines match
  the offer window and vanilla item cards (was showing raw values).
- Tighter, personality-aware neutral haggle baseline + Neutral Haggle Tightness slider.
- Simplified "Making an Offer" tutorial text.
- CHIM: send effective standing and make server reactions relationship-aware
  (disliked merchants stay curt, beloved warm up; standing woven into memory).
- Add font assets for upcoming UI theme system.
